rows.label: qst702301_msg0001
rows.name:
Say, have you met a soldier called
Meknes by any chance? He's my
subordinate, but he's gone AWOL.

rows.label: qst702301_msg0002
rows.name:
...I swear, he never struck me as
the type to just leave. I thought
he had more integrity than that...

rows.label: qst702301_msg0003
rows.name:
If you hear any news, no matter how
trivial, could you let me know?

rows.label: qst702301_msg0004
rows.name:
No ships have left the harbor lately,
so I imagine he'll still be in Iira.
Maybe he left for the capital...?

rows.label: qst702301_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe he just...lost his way...?
At least, let's hope so...
